OL,3,CJohn Swinney rules out talks with
OL,4,CReform as new MSPs arrive at Holyrood
OL,6,FSNP leader John Swinney has said he
OL,7,Fwill seek talks with the leaders of
OL,8,Fpolitical parties in Holyrood in a bid
OL,9,Fto foster better relations, but will
OL,10,Fnot work with Reform.
OL,12,FThe SNP secured a fifth consecutive
OL,13,Fwin at Holyrood in the May 7 elections
OL,14,Fbut fell short of the 65-seat
OL,15,Fmajority, although Swinney is on
OL,16,Fcourse to be reappointed as First
OL,17,FMinister in a vote next week to
OL,18,Fofficially re-elect him to the post.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
