PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778533866
OL,3,CJohn Swinney rules out talks with
OL,4,CReform as new MSPs arrive at Holyrood
OL,6,FScotland's newest MSPs arrived for
OL,7,Ftheir first day at Holyrood on Monday
OL,8,Fwith some 64 new faces walking the
OL,9,Fhalls of the Edinburgh parliament
OL,10,Ffollowing Friday's results.
OL,12,FOne of the newly-elected number is
OL,13,Fcurrent SNP MP Stephen Gethins, who is
OL,14,Fset to resign his Arbroath and
OL,15,FBroughty Ferry seat at Westminster to
OL,16,Fsit in Holyrood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
