PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778533866
OL,3,CJohn Swinney rules out talks with
OL,4,CReform as new MSPs arrive at Holyrood
OL,6,FThe First Minister was greeted at the
OL,7,FScottish government's base at St
OL,8,FAndrews House in Edinburgh by the
OL,9,Fcountry's top civil servant, Permanent
OL,10,FSecretary Joe Griffin. More than 100
OL,11,Fcivil servants applauded in the lobby
OL,12,Fof the building as the First Minister
OL,13,Farrived on Monday morning.
OL,15,FSpeaking as he wrote to the leaders of
OL,16,Fthe four other parties in Holyrood on
OL,17,FMonday, Swinney said: "The SNP
OL,18,Fgovernment has been emphatically re-
OL,19,Felected, but it is right that we now
OL,20,Flook to find common ground.
OL,26,@yD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778533866
OL,3,CJohn Swinney rules out talks with
OL,4,CReform as new MSPs arrive at Holyrood
OL,6,F"I am, today, urging every party other
OL,7,Fthan Reform UK to work openly and
OL,8,Fconstructively with us in the national
OL,9,Finterest ` and I give my assurance
OL,10,Fthat my government will operate on a
OL,11,Fbasis of cross-party co-operation.
OL,13,F"But I have been very clear ` we will
OL,14,Fhave absolutely nothing to do with
OL,15,FReform UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778533866
OL,3,CJohn Swinney rules out talks with
OL,4,CReform as new MSPs arrive at Holyrood
OL,6,F"They have nothing to offer the people
OL,7,Fof Scotland, I fundamentally disagree
OL,8,Fwith their values and many of those
OL,9,Fwho have been elected to represent
OL,10,Fthem have expressed reprehensible
OL,11,Fviews.
OL,13,F"I said during the election campaign
OL,14,Fthat we would lock them out of
OL,15,Finfluence in the Scottish Parliament
OL,16,Fand that is exactly what I will do.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778533866
OL,3,CJohn Swinney rules out talks with
OL,4,CReform as new MSPs arrive at Holyrood
OL,6,F"Our focus will be delivering the
OL,7,Fmanifesto on which we were so
OL,8,Femphatically elected, and I look
OL,9,Fforward to working cooperatively with
OL,10,Fother parties on these plans."
OL,12,FSpeaking to the BBC, Reform UK
OL,13,FScotland's deputy leader Thomas Kerr
OL,14,Faccused the First Minister of
OL,15,F"political posturing".
OL,17,F"We've not even stepped foot in the
OL,18,Fchamber yet," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@^O]wD@AOUwD@UO]yD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778533866
OL,3,CJohn Swinney rules out talks with
OL,4,CReform as new MSPs arrive at Holyrood
OL,6,F"These are politicians who are doing
OL,7,Fpolitical posturing before we've even
OL,8,Fstepped foot in the chambers of the
OL,9,FHolyrood Parliament.
OL,11,F"So, I think it's ridiculous for them,
OL,12,Fit's anti democratic, we've seen this
OL,13,Flast year when John Swinney held his
OL,14,Fanti-democratic summit, it backfired
OL,15,Fon him then... this will backfire on
OL,16,Fhim."
